The Hon Dr Craig Emerson MP, Minister for Small Business, Independent Contractors and the Service Economy gives this lecture - One Australia, one market: challenges for productivity policy - at The Australian National University on 6 July 2010.The talk was the first HC Coombs Policy Forum lecture and was presented by the Australian National Institute for Public Policy.
